review.reviewBody: tasty homestyle pasta dishes full of flavour.
Food court quality spaghetti and meatballs.

Flavourless Gnocchi Cream Rose, bland, barely any sauce on the Tagliatelle Bolognese Pasta, Caprese Salad was an insulting portion and comical bite sized pieces, never heard of this place wanted to give it a try, support local, spaghetti factory could beat this.   Vergogna su di te.
The Fried Calamari is good though I'd suggest having the option of Tzatziki sauce . which they only gave a piece of lemon .
I had the Fettuccine Al Salmone and it was wonderful. The portion size was perfect for me and the sauce was great too. I'll order again!
